Invocation Name: wind stream
Developer Terms of Use
des:
"OfficeSuite UC® is a 100 percent cloud-based unified communications solution, offering unmatched security, mobility and control for your office phone system. Windstream for Alexa integrates OfficeSuite UC and Amazon Alexa to offer hands free solutions for updating your call settings and managing your voicemails.

Features: 

• Turn on or off do not disturb 
• Turn on or off call twinning 
• Update your call forwarding settings – point calls to a new extension, auto attendant or voicemail
• Listen to and manage your voicemails 
• Make OfficeSuite UC calls
